<h2 class="Headline">Rust 1.97.0 released</h2>
        
        <div class="BlurbListing">
        <span class="Smaller">[Development] Posted Jul 9, 2026 13:19 UTC (Thu) by corbet</span>
        <p>
        <a href="https://blog.rust-lang.org/2026/07/09/Rust-1.97.0/">Version
1.97.0</a> of the Rust programming language has been released.  Changes
include using a new symbol-mangling scheme by default, support for denying
warnings in Cargo, and an end to the practice of hiding the linker's output
after a successful build.
